OL,3,CGuernsey Election: What you need to
OL,4,Cknow
OL,6,FWant the inside track on the issues
OL,7,Fthat will shape Guernsey's Election
OL,8,Fthis June? Listen to Guernsey Votes,
OL,9,Fan ITV Channel podcast packed with
OL,10,Fexpert guests, local insight and
OL,11,Fanalysis you can trust...
OL,13,FWhen I first arrived in Guernsey just
OL,14,Fshy of ten months ago, I was instantly
OL,15,Fstruck by the unique little quirks
OL,16,Fthis island has. Think filter in
OL,17,Fturns, hedge veg, blue postboxes and
OL,18,Fof course, the ever familiar
OL,19,Fpleasantry - 'cheerie!'
