OL,3,CGuernsey Election: What you need to
OL,4,Cknow
OL,6,FIt's fair to say I quickly realised
OL,7,Fpolitics was certainly amongst that
OL,8,Flist of quirks, albeit in a slightly
OL,9,Fless charming way, and for a political
OL,10,Fanimal like myself, I couldn't wait to
OL,11,Fwork out why!
OL,13,FIt's partly to do with the system
OL,14,Fitself (which I'll come onto!), but
OL,15,Falso the unique challenges and issues
OL,16,Fon this small yet beautiful rock in
OL,17,Fthe middle of the English Channel.
