OL,4,Cknow
OL,6,FQuestions that dominate discussion
OL,7,Ftend to revolve around reducing the
OL,8,Fhuge price of getting on and off our
OL,9,Fislands, building more housing and
OL,10,Flowering costs, improving
OL,11,Faccessibility for people who may have
OL,12,Fa disability, filling the huge skills
OL,13,Fgap in a lot of our key industries and
OL,14,Fhow the island finds the money to fund
OL,15,Fitself.
