OL,4,Cknow
OL,6,FThese help guide the mantras of
OL,7,Fpoliticians throughout terms but with
OL,8,Fa range of candidates standing in the
OL,9,Fupcoming election, there's a risk of
OL,10,Fan information overload for the
OL,11,Fgeneral public.
OL,13,FKey election dates:
OL,15,FGuernsey's political process has
OL,16,Fundergone a lot of change over the
OL,17,Fyears, especially around how elections
OL,18,Fwork. The introduction of an 'island-
OL,19,Fwide' system last time around has led
OL,20,Fto outsiders describing it as the
OL,21,F'strangest' election in the world.
