OL,3,CGuernsey Election: What you need to
OL,4,Cknow
OL,6,FThat might be to do with the fact that
OL,7,Feach voter has up to 38 votes to cast.
OL,8,FYes, 38! As a journalist covering the
OL,9,FUK General Election last year, when
OL,10,Fmany found it hard to place their
OL,11,Fconfidence in just one candidate, the
OL,12,Fprospect of marking your ballot that
OL,13,Fmany times is unfathomable and for
OL,14,Fmany can be laborious and extremely
OL,15,Fdifficult.
