OL,6,FIn their bid to win votes, each
OL,7,Fcandidate puts together two pages
OL,8,Fworth of a manifesto, which is
OL,9,Fassembled together in a booklet
OL,10,Fdistributed to each household ahead of
OL,11,Fthe poll. At the last election in
OL,12,F2020, the booklet was 222 pages long!
