OL,3,CGuernsey Election: What you need to
OL,4,Cknow
OL,6,FThe 38 candidates with the most votes
OL,7,Fare elected to the States and as the
OL,8,Fmargin between them is likely to be
OL,9,Fcomparatively narrow, you can
OL,10,Funderstand why there were recounts
OL,11,Flast time around. It's then a waiting
OL,12,Fgame for the public as the elected
OL,13,Fpoliticians decide amongst themselves
OL,14,Fwho will take the top jobs.
