OL,3,CGuernsey Election: What you need to
OL,4,Cknow
OL,6,FIt became clear going into this
OL,7,Felection cycle, there was a need for a
OL,8,Fdeep, analytical dive into the crucial
OL,9,Fpolitical decisions that affect the
OL,10,Fisland now and going forward. We hope
OL,11,Four podcast, 'Guernsey Votes', gets to
OL,12,Fthe crux of these issues and helps
OL,13,Fvoters to stay informed alongside
OL,14,Flighter moments.
OL,16,FWe will be speaking to islanders, none
OL,17,Fof whom are candidates, about why
OL,18,Fthese issues affect them and what they
OL,19,Fwant to see out of their politicians
OL,20,Fin the next political term.
