OL,6,FWe've got experts in their field such
OL,7,Fas business people, those who have
OL,8,Fworked in the education system,
OL,9,Fyounger voters and even a former
OL,10,Fdeputy.
OL,12,FBut given the short time I've been on
OL,13,Fthe island, coupled with my limited
OL,14,Fbackground knowledge, I hope to go on
OL,15,Fthe journey with you, learning more
OL,16,Fabout the issues that matter.
